title: Nile - What Should Not Be Unearthed (2015) 320ak
description:
What Should Not Be Unearthed is the upcoming eighth studio album by American technical death metal band Nile. The album will be released on August 28, 2015, in North America through Nuclear Blast.

On 7 July, 2015, the album's track-listing was revealed.

On 24 July, 2015, the album's first lyric video for the track "Call to Destruction" was released.
